</a></p>","position":1,"fullName":"content:wysiwyg_basic:1:40","htmlElement":"html","primarytype":"content","id":"content:wysiwyg_basic:1:40","styles":{},"newLoc":"design:columns:3 Columns:4:98-1:3 Columns:1","contentOverride":false}}},"design:columns:3 Columns:4:98-1:3 Columns:2":{"width":1,"html":"<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">*</div>","classes":"col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12","droppable":true,"children":{"content:images:0:15":{"icon":"images","name":"Image","type":"images","description":"Reference to image ZUIDs in Zesty.io","html":"<img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://apps.zesty.io/freestyle/images/images-placeholder.jpg\" alt=\"placeholder\" />","draggable":true,"content":"https://apps.zesty.io/freestyle/images/images-placeholder.jpg","position":0,"fullName":"content:images:0:15","htmlElement":"img","primarytype":"content","newLoc":"design:columns:3 Columns:4:98-1:3 Columns:2","oldLoc":"bank"},"content:wysiwyg_basic:1:71":{"icon":"outdent","name":"WYSIWYG","type":"wysiwyg_basic","html":"<h3>Professional Impact</h3>\n<p></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://volunteer.central.salvationarmyusa.org/?tags=Professional%2520%252B%2520Skilled%2520Services\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Professional + Skilled Services</a></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://volunteer.central.salvationarmyusa.org/?tags=Court-Mandated%2520Opportunities\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Court-Mandated</a></p>","description":"Text with HTML references.","draggable":true,"content":"<h3>Professional Impact</h3>\n<p></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://volunteer.central.salvationarmyusa.org/?tags=Professional%2520%252B%2520Skilled%2520Services\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Professional + Skilled Services</a></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://volunteer.central.salvationarmyusa.org/?tags=Court-Mandated%2520Opportunities\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Court-Mandated</a></p>","position":1,"fullName":"content:wysiwyg_basic:1:71","htmlElement":"html","primarytype":"content","id":"content:wysiwyg_basic:1:71","styles":{},"newLoc":"design:columns:3 Columns:4:98-1:3 Columns:2","contentOverride":false}}}},"primarytype":"design","newLoc":"layout:root:column:0","oldLoc":"bank"},"content:wysiwyg_basic:4:35:5:31:6:31":{"icon":"outdent","name":"35","type":"wysiwyg_basic","html":"<h2>A Smarter Way to Serve</h2>\n<p></p>\n<p>Our platform is built to respect your time and simplify your journey. Enjoy a modern interface that offers:</p>\n<p></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Precision Filtering: </strong>Customize your search by <strong>ZIP code</strong>, specific<strong> days of the week</strong>, or time of day (<strong>Morning, Afternoon, or Evening</strong>).</li>\n<li>Personalized Experience: Your volunteer profile automatically saves your preferences and prioritizes opportunities within 50 miles of home, ensuring you stay connected to your local community. Adjust the radius to see opportunities within <strong>5 to 100 miles</strong> of home.</li>\n<li><strong>Group Coordination: </strong>Real-time <strong>Capacity </strong>tracking allows you to see exactly how many spots are available for your group or family.</li>\n<li><strong>Total Flexibility: </strong>Manage your own schedule. Register for, change, or cancel your shifts directly through your profile—no phone calls or emails required.</li>\n<li><strong>On-Demand Records: </strong>Instantly track your hours and download <strong>official service certificates</strong> for school, work, or legal requirements.</li>\n</ul>","description":"Text with HTML references.","draggable":true,"content":"<h2>A Smarter Way to Serve</h2>\n<p></p>\n<p>Our platform is built to respect your time and simplify your journey. Enjoy a modern interface that offers:</p>\n<p></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Precision Filtering: </strong>Customize your search by <strong>ZIP code</strong>, specific<strong> days of the week</strong>, or time of day (<strong>Morning, Afternoon, or Evening</strong>).</li>\n<li>Personalized Experience: Your volunteer profile automatically saves your preferences and prioritizes opportunities within 50 miles of home, ensuring you stay connected to your local community. Adjust the radius to see opportunities within <strong>5 to 100 miles</strong> of home.</li>\n<li><strong>Group Coordination: </strong>Real-time <strong>Capacity </strong>tracking allows you to see exactly how many spots are available for your group or family.</li>\n<li><strong>Total Flexibility: </strong>Manage your own schedule. Register for, change, or cancel your shifts directly through your profile—no phone calls or emails required.</li>\n<li><strong>On-Demand Records: </strong>Instantly track your hours and download <strong>official service certificates</strong> for school, work, or legal requirements.</li>\n</ul>","model":"4","position":5,"fullName":"content:wysiwyg_basic:4:35:5:31:6:31","htmlElement":"html","primarytype":"content","id":"content:wysiwyg_basic:4:35:5:31:6:31","styles":{},"newLoc":"layout:root:column:0","contentOverride":false},"content:wysiwyg_basic:4:25:5:57:6:90":{"icon":"outdent","name":"25","type":"wysiwyg_basic","html":"<h2>Specialized Paths to Service</h2>\n<p></p>\n<p>Whether you are serving with a professional team or fulfilling specific requirements, our platform is designed to accommodate your unique needs.</p>\n<p></p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><strong>Corporate &amp; Employee Engagement: </strong>Build team culture while giving back to your community. To begin planning a custom service activity for your organization, visit our <a href=\"https://www.salvationarmyusa.org/usa-central-territory/corporate-volunteer-opportunities\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Corporate Engagement Page</a> to learn more and submit an inquiry to our team.</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><strong>Court-Mandated Service: </strong>We provide a transparent way to fulfill and document required service hours. All court-mandated volunteers must follow a specific registration process and complete required documentation. Visit our <a href=\"https://www.salvationarmyusa.org/usa-central-territory/court-mandated-volunteer-opportunities\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Court-Mandated Service Page</a> for the step-by-step guide and necessary forms to begin.</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><strong>Skilled &amp; Professional Support: </strong>Put your career experience to work. From marketing and IT to legal and administrative support, filter to <a href=\"https://volunteer.central.salvationarmyusa.org/?tags=Professional%2520%252B%2520Skilled%2520Services\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Professional + Skilled Services</a> to find high-impact roles that match your specific expertise.</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><strong>Community Groups: </strong>Bringing a club, church group, or a circle of friends? Use the Capacity filter on our portal to instantly see opportunities with enough open spots for your entire crew</li>\n</ul>","description":"Text with HTML references.","draggable":true,"content":"<h2>Specialized Paths to Service</h2>\n<p></p>\n<p>Whether you are serving with a professional team or fulfilling specific requirements, our platform is designed to accommodate your unique needs.</p>\n<p></p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><strong>Corporate &amp; Employee Engagement: </strong>Build team culture while giving back to your community. To begin planning a custom service activity for your organization, visit our <a href=\"https://www.salvationarmyusa.org/usa-central-territory/corporate-volunteer-opportunities\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Corporate Engagement Page</a> to learn more and submit an inquiry to our team.</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><strong>Court-Mandated Service: </strong>We provide a transparent way to fulfill and document required service hours. All court-mandated volunteers must follow a specific registration process and complete required documentation. Visit our <a href=\"https://www.salvationarmyusa.org/usa-central-territory/court-mandated-volunteer-opportunities\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Court-Mandated Service Page</a> for the step-by-step guide and necessary forms to begin.</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><strong>Skilled &amp; Professional Support: </strong>Put your career experience to work. From marketing and IT to legal and administrative support, filter to <a href=\"https://volunteer.central.salvationarmyusa.org/?tags=Professional%2520%252B%2520Skilled%2520Services\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Professional + Skilled Services</a> to find high-impact roles that match your specific expertise.</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><strong>Community Groups: </strong>Bringing a club, church group, or a circle of friends? Use the Capacity filter on our portal to instantly see opportunities with enough open spots for your entire crew</li>\n</ul>","model":"4","position":6,"fullName":"content:wysiwyg_basic:4:25:5:57:6:90","htmlElement":"html","primarytype":"content","id":"content:wysiwyg_basic:4:25:5:57:6:90","styles":{},"newLoc":"layout:root:column:0","contentOverride":false},"content:block:6-98dac4fd85-s1lt65:6:98":{"html":"<div>{{block('/-/block/generic_image_text_button_block.html?variant=7-a8d1a3de81-jd4bzb')}}</div>","content":"{{block('/-/block/generic_image_text_button_block.html?variant=7-a8d1a3de81-jd4bzb')}}","model":"6-98dac4fd85-s1lt65","name":"Generic Image Text Button Block","position":7,"fullName":"content:block:6-98dac4fd85-s1lt65:6:98","type":"block","primarytype":"content","newLoc":"layout:root:column:0","oldLoc":"bank","id":"content:block:6-98dac4fd85-s1lt65:6:98","styles":{},"contentOverride":false},"content:wysiwyg_basic:7:58":{"icon":"outdent","name":"WYSIWYG","type":"wysiwyg_basic","html":"<h2>Explore by Region</h2>\n<p></p>\n<p>If you prefer to connect directly with volunteer staff in your area, select your region below:]</p>\n<ul>\n<li>IndianaKansas &amp; Western Missouri<br>Michigan<br>Minnesota &amp; North Dakota<br>Missouri &amp; Southern Illinois<br>North &amp; Central Illinois<br>South Dakota, Iowa, &amp; Nebraska<br>Wisconsin &amp; Upper Michigan</li>\n</ul>","description":"Text with HTML references.","draggable":true,"content":"<h2>Explore by Region</h2>\n<p></p>\n<p>If you prefer to connect directly with volunteer staff in your area, select your region below:]</p>\n<ul>\n<li>IndianaKansas &amp; Western Missouri<br>Michigan<br>Minnesota &amp; North Dakota<br>Missouri &amp; Southern Illinois<br>North &amp; Central Illinois<br>South Dakota, Iowa, &amp; Nebraska<br>Wisconsin &amp; Upper Michigan</li>\n</ul>","position":7,"fullName":"content:wysiwyg_basic:7:58","htmlElement":"html","primarytype":"content","id":"content:wysiwyg_basic:7:58","styles":{},"newLoc":"layout:root:column:0","contentOverride":false}}}}